    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to &quot;Doge Head Attack&quot;! An exciting platformer inspired by Memecoins. Embark on an epic adventure through four unique levels, filled with challenges and mini-games that will test your skills. This meme-inspired game features plenty of jokes and humor to keep you entertained!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Epic Adventures:</strong> Explore themed levels with vibrant graphics and challenging obstacles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fun Mini-Games:</strong> Earn extra lives and discover hidden secrets in each level.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Intuitive Controls:</strong> Designed for a smooth gaming experience across all platforms.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Levels:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level 1:</strong> Face the boss <strong>FLOKY</strong> and overcome the initial obstacles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level 2:</strong> Challenge the cunning <strong>PEPE</strong> in his domain.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level 3:</strong> Prepare for the powerful <strong>DOGE</strong> and his unpredictable tricks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level 4:</strong> A surprise level that will amaze players with new challenges.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Download &quot;Doge Head Attack&quot; now and join the fun!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controls:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >D: Right.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A: Left.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >K: Shoot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >J: Jump.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ESC: Pause.</p>",
